title: Leg Medium Skin Tone
description: Represents a prosthetic leg with a medium skin tone, often used to signify prosthetics, disability representation, or a person in motion.
apple_vendor_description: On Apple devices, this leg emoji showcases a smooth, medium skin tone with a subtle sheen that highlights its rounded contours and realistic form. The gentle 3D shading and soft edges contribute to its lifelike appearance, making it feel approachable and humanistic. It's commonly used to represent movement, travel, or the physical act of walking and standing, conveying a sense of personal presence in digital conversations.
